Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another sniper...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they shoot from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Withdraw via route C immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shot that didn't hit anyone but stirred up mistrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how will the heroine improvise her way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called us all the way out here to get shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys will pay for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you bastards the ones who shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Mr. Godoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, let's retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinate has successfully erased the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry about snipings anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What they hell are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Godoh, I present to you Issac Wisemel's head.\NThe head of the person who has been plotting to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This traitor, who only cares about personal profit, was killed by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reason for shooting our own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sniping was plotted by Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you confirm the identity of the sniper who my subordinate stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that would be unshakable evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice set-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Inferno way of settling things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel sniping occurred after I killed Randy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't part of Wisemel's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was another sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sniper was also Wisemel's subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type that's extremely determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did the sniper only fire one shot and didn't continue to fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel's objective should have been to kill Godoh Daisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you're the only one who knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing or not killing... didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sniper's true objective was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to stir up mistrust between the two groups there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To mess up Inferno from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they even predict that Claudia would kill Wisemel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole thing is a conspiracy stirred up by that bastard Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Clau finished him off according to her own judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in thinking that deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzy's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if Wisemel takes the blame for everything that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whereabouts of the 5 million becomes clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money that the Godoh Clan lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will appear in Wisemel's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will put an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deaths of the yakuza, avenging Judy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my very own assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard some rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Issac of the Bloodies died?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person you killed was Issac's man and also the one who killed Judy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then avenging Judy is done...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was my assassin training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's fine with you, I can help you with your assassinations from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean I'm fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to miss your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I'll let you be my kitchen maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Yay! A maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid clothes are really cute, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! No maid clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay as long as I can stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fabulous report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sums up that Issac Wisemel was behind everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godoh Clan has no reason not to consent to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, to be able to see through all this in the middle of such chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be taking Issac's place from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disappoint me, Claudia McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She has a rare quality about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent... I've heard such words before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean you want to train that girl into a hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't show any results...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what to expect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's see what she's made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any more dangers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should find an excuse and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...send her off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel at ease when I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be coming back the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably should have told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry. Have a good trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're already used to the office work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about just spending your days like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already an executive.\NThere's no need to wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still hasn't ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you need?\NBeing too greedy will do you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know you won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful where you tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I seem that much of an idiot to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me give you some advice. It's my hobby, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, I didn't really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the full one you-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back! You're home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken served with this is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I just let this go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to become your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you don't want me to become an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you know the pain of an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to become useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being weak, being poor, and not being able to do anything without relying on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of living like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, you can walk whatever path you want. Do whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you want to become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you hate yourself too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing is like my second nature and I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to become like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Reiji... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many have died because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't there, they would still be living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could have all gone back to their families and lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just accepted a job that was going to be done either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as pretty as you described...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you really want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you shoot just because you want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel bitter, full of pain, sad, and unforgiving to yourself for doing such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't pull the trigger simply like the people that killed Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live while enduring it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you won't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't kill the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those guys back then had been you, then Judy wouldn't have had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you kill your first person, the whole world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you see... everything you hear... everything changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be your kind self anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't come into the world that I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But you'll always stay in there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go there, then I'll always be able to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really do want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing that, I can stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need. I'll go to your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go... Let me go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the world where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, I was like a dead person before I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get split up, I'll turn into a dead person again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forget how to laugh and cry.\NThe things you made me remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, this guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it. It's that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. McCunnen should've been helping you people join Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was the plan changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the boss immediately! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn should be over soon, Ms. McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a flower that's suitable for the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom, can you dispatch right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The remnants of the Bloodies are making some weird movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to settle it without causing a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Where do we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual train station at 20:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we would be together for the whole day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to be together forever from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to regain my own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Cal's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Elen. I'm Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter now or before. I'm just Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
